item.title: CVE-2020-7817|2024-08-04T09:41:01.850Z -- activesoft -- mybrowserplus
item.description: MyBrowserPlus downloads the files needed to run the program through the setup file (Setup.inf). At this time, there is a vulnerability in downloading arbitrary files due to insufficient integrity verification of the files.
